Notes
-----

This CVar should only be enabled when used with [DX9 class](Vertex\_and\_fragment\_programs) video cards. Even so it might be advantageous to disable this CVar if your video card is low-end and/or if you have a very fast CPU in which case the original method might still prove to be faster.


